metadata.name: The Blocks #1
metadata.description: The Blocks Genesis NFT is built with a long-term business and community in mind – “Mr. Block.” Mr. Block is a community-grown knowledge hub to educate, onboard, and enable the blockchain ecosystem and next generation of crypto participants. As a holder of The Blocks Genesis NFT, you’re joining a passionate community of education ambassadors for the blockchain ecosystem, ready to onboard and empower new participants into Web3 and Crypto.
